        <span class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 via-orange-500 to-yellow-400"></span>
        <span class="absolute inset-0 x66-cta-shine"></span>
        <span class="relative flex items-center gap-1.5 drop-shadow-md">
          <span class="text-base">🎰</span>
          <span class="tracking-wide">ĐĂNG KÝ TÀI KHOẢN XOSO66</span>
